citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
Section 2.126(b) - A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection
process at 11am on 01/14/2016. The inspector attempted to make contact by knocking on the door, calling and
waiting 30 minutes.
